summary: Our vision is to care for the children in need in the villages and slums of DR Congo. Children without a caring family are extremely vulnerable. We want to be family to them, giving the care and protection they need. We want to see the God given dignity of these children being restored by having access to education, food and health care, and by knowing their Father in Heaven through discipleship. We want to see darkness impacted by the light of Godâ€™s presence.
